description: Experience elevated living in this stunning 11th-floor residence. This elegant 2-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers sweeping views of Boston Harbor from both the living room and primary bedroom. Designed for the entertaining homeowner, the gourmet kitchen features Wolf and Sub-Zero appliances, a wine fridge and marble countertops—all accented by custom Italian cabinetry from BAMO. Thoughtfully appointed with ample storage, a dedicated laundry, custom handcrafted hardware, Sherle Wagner International bath fixtures, and Phillip Jeffries wall coverings, this home seamlessly blends function with sophistication. Residents enjoy access to top-tier amenities including an indoor pool, hot tub, sauna, steam room, spa, state-of-the-art fitness center, and a harbor-facing grand lounge. 24-concierge and door attendant included.
